{"tid":1240122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整場運動係我哋呢班年青人救咗香港","createTime":"2019-06-18T09:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T09:41:07.000Z","uid":104096,"like":76,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"483ebb00950c15bb9c79640b4ccb2a7498aa8b4a","tid":1240122,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:20:48.000Z","msg":"我哋由5月已經開始打文宣<br />\n用咗好多前人無諗過嘅方法<br />\n利用而家有嘅技術盡量spread出去<br />\n集合眾人之力<br />\n結果兩次遊行再次破紀錄<br />\n612我哋企到最前<br />\n但我哋無害怕<br />\n連日嚟大家通宵頂完又頂、撐完又撐<br />\n可以逼到政府短時間唔敢放上枱再講送中<br />\n我對大家感到非常驕傲<br />\n但場戰爭仲未完結<br />\n大家如果覺得好攰無心機<br />\n不妨拎返黑警啲片嚟睇、睇柒婆個柒頭樣黑口黑面<br />\n甚至係諗起太古廣場嘅義士，以生命作出最高層次嘅犧牲<br />\n我哋一定要堅持落去<br />\n年青人係香港嘅將來<br />\n完全唔到班廢老話事<br />\n我哋要堅持自己相信嘅價值<br />\n唔可以令整個6月做嘅嘢白白浪費<br />\n各位加油，星期五見<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsVQA2U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsVQA2U.jpg&h=0fe5ceb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"061c976888e2134d103c4ac804f907adfc3cdb7a","tid":1240122,"uid":104096,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:21:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">抗爭到底</span></span>"},{"pid":"902dd4c8264a8be75f4177bb677fc700efb41aa8","tid":1240122,"uid":164626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"63de8c02a6c3d7d045da2f29efa0bd8273f7a013","tid":1240122,"uid":104096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:24:18.000Z","msg":"大家要堅持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />革命仲未成功"},{"pid":"8e088175a8c0f10161dd29539ab40c3d862e1014","tid":1240122,"uid":199989,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:29:08.000Z","msg":"唔好分化 全香港人都有努力"},{"pid":"23c110f481e2159a810ef158f73af93d89c394f0","tid":1240122,"uid":1534